Title: Precious Metal
Plot: Catherine, Nick and Sara investigate a seemingly months old body found in the mountains. Warrick and Grissom look into the case of a man found murdered in an alley, but the medical examiner 'loses' the body for 11 days.
GuestStars: Katherine La Nasa, Matt Winston, Garret Dillahunt, Matt DeCaro, Blake Adams, Sarah Lancaster, Pippi Boecher, Chris Crotty, Wiley Pickett, Craig Welzbecher
